'''Broken Gate''' was a form of unarmed combat practiced by the [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

Some of the techniques used in this form included [[Wikipedia:Punch (strike)|striking]], [[Wikipedia:Throw (grappling)|throwing]], and [[Wikipedia:Stomp (strike)|stomping]].

It is possible that Broken Gate also utilized [[Wikipedia:Joint lock|joint locking]] techniques, as [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Ilena Xan]], the unarmed combat instructor at the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]], was a specialist in joint locking. [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Tallisibeth Enwandung-Esterhazy]], one of Ilena Xan's students, was also known for being skilled in joint locking.

